sidiary of ronald perelmans macandrews  forbes the buyout—engineered with the help of junk bond king michael p milken—saddled revlon with a huge  billion debt load which became an albatross around the companys neck for years to come pantry pride inc offered to buy any or all of revlons  million outstanding shares for  a share when its street price stood at  a share initially rejected he repeatedly raised his offer until it reached  a share while fighting revlons management every step of the way forstmann little  company swooped in at  a share a brief public bidding war ensued and perelman triumphed with an offer of  a share perelman paid  billion to revlons shareholders but he also paid  million of other costs associated with the purchase perelman had revlon sell four divisions two for  billion the vision care division for  million and the national health laboratories division which became a publicly owned corporation in  additional makeup lines were purchased for revlon max factor in  and betrix in  later sold to procter  gamble in  also in  revlon sold the clean  clear brand to johnson  johnson in march  revlon acquired mirage cosmetics makers of sinful colors nail products in  peta removed revlon and other highprofile cosmetic brands from its list of companies who do not test their products on animals after the organization learned they were paying chinese laboratories to test their cosmetics on rabbits and other animals in august  revlon consumer products corp bought the colomer group from cvc capital partners a private equity firm for  million after suffering business loss in  and  at the end of  revlon announced that it will exit the chinese market which employs  people the business in china accounted for just  percent portion of net sales of revlons international operations on november   revlon named lorenzo delpani as president and ceo  on september   revlons board of directors elected roberto simon as executive vice president and chief financial officer effective as of sept  advertisingedit tram with revlon advertising in hong kong june  up until the s revlons magazine ads were drawn by hand and mostly in black and white beginning in  revlon began launching fullcolor photographic advertisements in major magazines and stores across the country revlon introduced matching nail polish and lipsticks with exotic and unique names these ads were taken by the top fashion photographers of the day including richard avedon cecil beaton and john rawlings some of these ads were for paint the town pink and s fatal apple with dorian leigh in  revlon introduced bachelors carnation and in  sweet talk in  revlon introduced a red lipstick and nail enamel called wheres the fire revlon used the word fire again later in their fire and ice ads one of the worlds first supermodels dorian leigh starred in some of revlons most memorable advertisements of all time in  dorian was covered in purple flowers and wrapped in a pale purple sheet for ultra violet in  dorian appeared in fashion plate in  at the age of  she appeared in cherries in the snow later that year she appeared in the legendary fire and ice ad shot by richard avedon originally dorian appeared in a tight silverbeaded dress with an enormous red wrap her black hair had a silver swirl in it and she had her hands with long red nails positioned in front of her breasts charles revson rejected avedons original ad as too sexual they reshot the ad this time with her open hand in front of one hip the other in front of her cheek the advertisement became madison avenue legend because of the fullpage quiz next to the sensual ad almost  years later in november  revlon recreated s fire and ice magazine ad this time with actress jessica biel with this ad revlon announced they were issuing a limited edition fire and ice lipstick and nail color calling this campaign lips and tips dorian leighs yearsyounger redheaded sister suzy parker also shot numerous revlon magazine ads in the s charles revson who wanted to marry dorian at some point despised suzy and vice versa at one point he refused to hire her anymore because suzy complained about the peanut paycheck she received from revlon richard avedon however after photographing other models for a particular revlon ad would call in suzy last minute sometimes late at night to do retakes with him this happened with stormy pink an ad suzy shot very late at night with a wild white horse in the ocean avedon would then tell revson that it was not suzy in the ad but a model named bubbles or another madeup name in  revlon became the first american cosmetics company to feature an african american model naomi sims in their advertising revlon was also noted for featuring models of a wide age range in the s including then yearold milla jovovich and then yearold audrey hepburn despite the successful campaigns of the s and s featuring models in particular cindy crawford revlon decided to drop fashion models and focus on movie stars among them kate bosworth jaime king halle berry susan sarandon melanie griffith julianne moore eva mendes jessica alba jennifer connelly beau garrett jessica biel olivia wilde emma stone and bond girls in  australian supermodel elle macpherson became a new spokesmodel for the company american actress jessica biel is the newest woman to model for the brand first shown in advertisements in january  main article list of revlon spokesmodels in  celebrity makeup artist gucci westman was hired as revlons global artistic director representing the company at runway shows and brand events and designing collections philanthropyedit becky gulsvig at revlon runwalk for cancer revlon is a corporate sponsor of several charity projects the largest of these is the revlon run walk a run and walk event held in new york and los angeles to raise money and awareness for breast and ovarian cancer revlon also supports other cancer charities such as look good feel better and the national breast cancer coalition and operates a mobile mammography clinic in and around oxford north carolina where the companys primary manufacturing operations are located in  revlon supported the development of a breast center at the university of california los angeles renamed revlonucla breast center the center is a wellknown institute for treatment and research of breast cancer and other breast diseases and disorders a revlon lip gloss shade whose proceeds support revlons cancer charities was also created in  in september  revlon with global artistic director gucci westman and spokesmodel halle berry hosted an event at fashions night out in new york city to raise funds for the jenesse center a los angeles organization for domestic violence victims revlon also hosted luncheons and various other events to benefit the center and partnered with online retailer drugstorecom to donate portions of lipstick sales to the organization see alsoedit list of revlon spokesmodels referencesedit  a b c financial statements for revlon  morningstar morningstarcom  retrieved    a b financials for revlon google finance  retrieved    fortune  page for revlon fortune  retrieved    model by michael gross  page   andrewtobiascom andrewtobiascom retrieved    mcgill douglas c august   cosmetics companies quietly ending animal tests the new york times   stevenson richard  pantry pride control of revlon board seen near new york times p d   macandrews  forbes holdings inc funding universe retrieved    revlon acquires sinful nail brand womens wear daily march     hills suzannah july   loccitane and yves rocher the bigname beauty brands among those ditching crueltyfree animal testing policies to sell their products to china daily mail retrieved  january    young vicki m revlon acquires colomer group for  million wwd retrieved  august    revlon to exit operations in china cut  jobs january     revlon names lorenzo delpani president ceo october     revlon inc announces election of roberto simon as executive vice president and chief financi